<section class="section-new-content" style="padding: 50px 0px;font-size:18px;color:#606060;">
  <div class="container">
    	<div id="blockStyle27952NewContent331" class="mob-text-p ccm-block-styles" >
<p class="mb-4">MHA provides services in some of the most ethnically diverse cities in the United Kingdom. We're proud to be part of the communities that are rich in ethnicity and cultural diversity. However, we recognise that every day, across the globe, ethnicity (or Race) can influence how a person is treated and can often lead to discrimination, bullying, and harassment.</p>
<p class="mb-8">We are working to ensure that our services and workplaces are an enjoyable environment for all employees and those that come into contact with our services.</p>
<p class="text-xl mb-4"><strong>Ethnicity and our workforce</strong></p></div>	<div id="blockStyle27944NewContent333" class="mb-4 mob-text-p ccm-block-styles" >

